Games::Sequential & Games::Sequential::Position
===============================================

These modules form an object-oriented framework for creating
sequential games in Perl.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module depends on Carp.

